==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Karat
<hw>Karat</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>the unit of measurement for the
proportion of gold in an alloy; 18-karat gold is 75 2.122e-314old;
24-karat gold is pure gold.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> carat.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

